high_descs: Turn around, move forward, then turn right, move forward, turn right, move forward, then turn left to approach the stove.
Pick up the pot on the back left range of the stove.
Turn right, move forward, turn right, move forward, then turn left to approach the fridge.
Chill the pot in the fridge.
Turn left, go straight, then turn left, go straight, then turn right to go to the stove.
Put the pot on the front left stove range.
anns.task_desc: Put a cool pot on the stove.

high_descs: turn left and cross the room to the stove
take the pot from the back left burner of the stove
turn right and cross the room to the refrigerator
open the refrigerator, place the pot on the middle shelf, and close the door. Wait seven seconds, and retrieve the pot, closing the refrigerator door afterward.
turn left and cross the room to the stove
place the pot on the front left burner of the stove
anns.task_desc: Place a cold pot on the front left burner on the stove.

high_descs: Go to the left and then to the right to stand in front of the stove.
Take the pot from the left side of the stove.
GO to the right and stand in front of the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the pot on the middle shelf, shut the door and open it again and take the pot out.
Go left and then left again to stand in front of the stove.
Put the pot on the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled pot on the stove.
